Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Voters back Bitburg visit
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xkt1
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 12 May 1985
President Reagan's visit to Bitburg military cemetery proves to be a political asset. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less